{
  "stem": "21812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We, we had-- my father had three brothers in the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we wrote to them, and they sent us the affidavits which would enable us to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were quota numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Each country had a quota number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It depended on the births-- of your place of birth, of what your quota number would be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Austria had a very large number, quota number, quota numbers, which allowed people to come to the United States if they had an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I believe it was 10,000 a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I might be mistaken, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But my father-- so my mother and I were born in, in Austria, so we fell under that quota.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father was born in Romania, which had a very, very small quota, about 290 people a year, because the Immigration Act that the United States enacted in '23 limited people from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so his chances of, of coming to the United States were nil, because we had a rough idea of what number was given at any one point-- and not exactly, but fairly close.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we knew that there would be no hope for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We knew that for us, there was a good possibility that we might make it, because we knew that war would start in the fall of '39.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was well known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Hitler didn't make it a secret.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were pretty sure that's when-- that was-- started wars in the fall, because it was a favorable time of year to start, to have the tanks, start the tanks to move.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we were pretty sure war would start then.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
